{"tid":1735843,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[純學術討論] 神秘火魔法 - 拜占庭希臘火","createTime":"2019-11-18T15:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T15:52:23.000Z","uid":20473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c93c76254a5aeb458d6a4cae4e15aa4d886b033a","tid":1735843,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"[純學術討論] 神秘火魔法 - 拜占庭希臘火<br />\n<br />\n東羅馬帝國(395-1453)能夠存在上千年,除左君士坦丁堡既厚實城壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰爭中擁有決定勝利甚至反敗為勝既武器都好重要<br />\n其中最神秘就係希臘火 Greek Fire<br />\n以下係維基link, 歷史自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E7%81%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B8%258C%25E8%2585%258A%25E7%2581%25AB&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=1eca35e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E7%81%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n因為拜占庭要保密,所以唔會公開希臘火制作方法, 甚至冇文獻記載準確成份<br />\n使用上主要係海戰, 因為佢有在水上燃燒,附著力強同不能用水救熄優點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於是海戰. 發射器會固定在船頭<br />\n經過用pump加壓, 利用氣泵將魔法液加壓. 加熱同虹吸管輸送魔法液噴出. <br />\n同時在噴咀點火, 就可以激射出火焰<br />\n溫度可達1000度及約50呎有效射程<br />\n<br />\nachieved a flame temperature of over 1,000 &deg;C (1,830 &deg;F) and an effective range of up to 15 meters (49 ft) (from wiki)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2iQhMz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2iQhMz.jpg&h=31e41566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://answersafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/greek-fire-gun-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanswersafrica.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Fgreek-fire-gun-640x360.jpg&h=ff79c41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9VNP50Cdkqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9VNP50Cdkqs&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=6dd257ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9VNP50Cdkqs</a><br />\n歷史學家仿製發射器,最尾激射高熱火燄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />PS. 火非常危險, 千祈唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}